.textarea
    h2 textarea
    h3 1.模板
    h5.demo 
      pre(hljs hljs-language="javascript")  
         | component-textarea(
         |    model="textarea"
         |    textareaName="textareaName" 
         |    placeholder="文本域"
         |    textareaClass="componentTextarea"
         |    maxlength="maxlength"
         |)
        
    h3 2.实例
    h5
      component-textarea(
          model="textareaModel"
          textareaName="textareaName" 
          placeholder="文本域"
          textareaClass="componentTextarea"
          maxlength="maxlength"
          ng-focus="focusEvent()"
          ng-blur="blurEvent()"
      )
      .self_input
          .leftWords 可输入的文字的最大长度
          input.maxLengthShow(ng-model="lengthValue" ng-change="inputChange()")
          .parent_add
              span.top(ng-click="topEvent()")
              span.bottom(ng-click="bottomEvent()")
      component-button.button(type='first' ng-click="clickEvent()" btn-name="打印文本框value值")
      .show {{textareaShow}}
    h3 3.描述
    h5
      |多行文本域组件是对原生testarea的封装
